data.description: Located in the desirable area of Red Mountain in NE Mesa, this single level home is not only spacious with 2,147 sq ft but it is also located on the second largest lot in the community!  Bedroom in front of house makes a great home office and has mountain views.  The living room/dining room is huge with plenty of room for entertaining.  Vaulted ceilings throughout - even in the bedrooms!  New flooring was installed throughout most of home! Perfectly located near numerous hiking trails and parks, Red Mountain Golf Course, Saguaro Lake Recreational Area, the Salt River wild horses and Usery Mountain Regional Park.
